,'2015-12-02 11:28:19',683,'2015-12-05 12:42:12',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',0,0,0),(70,'<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<a style=\"text-indent:2em;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">昨天晚上有个姑娘问我，冬天了有啥办法，能排解寂寞？</span></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我&nbsp;『寂寞的抚慰，孤独的守望，其实，都是饿。』</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">姑娘&nbsp;『so，你要给我做肉的了？』</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我&nbsp;『你是吃货吗？』</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">姑娘&nbsp;『必须是啊！！』</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我&nbsp;『吃货，就要敢于挑战一些不一样的。』</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">【苦瓜君】</span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/6/2/416/416_1449027126982.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">苦瓜，也叫半生瓜，味苦，味寒。不爱吃的人理由都很一致，爱吃的人越吃越有味。最爱料理苦瓜的省份就是广东，陈奕迅不是一首歌叫《苦瓜》：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">真想不到当初我们也讨厌吃苦瓜</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">今天竟吃得出那睿智愈来愈记挂</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">开始时捱一些苦&nbsp;栽种绝处的花</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">幸得艰辛的引路甜蜜不致太寡</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">到大悟大彻将虎咽的升华</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">至共你觉得苦也不太差</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">姑娘『苦瓜，有不苦的吗？</span><a></a><a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">』</span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我『吃黄瓜去呀。』</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>【苦瓜炒苦瓜】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">食神蔡澜先生早说过，那些个餐厅大厨，就喜欢把苦瓜在滚水里烫一遍再炒，苦味一点都没有了，是要咋？！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/7/0/417/417_1449027202926.png\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">所以，蔡澜便创出了“苦瓜炒苦瓜”这道菜！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">深绿、浅绿苦瓜各一条，切片。额，为什么要调颜色不一样的？没啥，容易分辨！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">深绿苦瓜在滚水灼一道，和全生的浅绿苦瓜一道入锅，怕苦？下点糖啊！最后加上蔡澜先生自家淘宝店咸鱼酱，么么哒！炒炒就完成了！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"380\" width=\"284\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">半生半灼的苦瓜味道如何？看网友</span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/1737632881\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">郝家胡胡</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">的晒图：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"385\" border=\"0\" width=\"519\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">图片一对比，大师的境界就知道了，对么！而且，没咸鱼酱，差评！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<a></a><a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">姑娘『苦瓜，能来点荤的么？』</span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>【奄仔蟹焖苦瓜】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">当然了，蔡澜先生炒鸡推荐下面这道奄仔蟹焖苦瓜，味道一流！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"314\" border=\"0\" width=\"421\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">奄仔蟹</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">台山奄仔蟹最好，膏香，肉实，而且鲜甜；蟹斩件，再和苦瓜一起炒，下蒜茸、豆豉炒個半生熟，入砂锅，再焗一下，就行了！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"144\" border=\"0\" width=\"230\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>苦瓜&amp;日本冲绳</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">你造吗？苦瓜要买冲绳苦瓜，最苦，而且分深浅两色。BUT，你造吗？明明是广东人先爱上的苦瓜，再传到日本冲绳，冲绳人民也惊艳到，原来苦瓜可以如此美味！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>【日本苦瓜派：一夫食堂】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">话说日本苦瓜代表，网红“一夫食堂”也有自己的一套做法！网红其实也是中国人的说，只不过在日本工作生活，家里还有一“饭模”，养活一家子的重任就靠饭模！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/8/1/418/418_1449027280942.png\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">饭模说了，家里苦瓜吃不完。。。拿过来，切大条，不能太细！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"368\" border=\"0\" width=\"276\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">沸水烫10秒，不能多不能少！捞出，趁热拌上酱油，少许香醋，白糖，味精！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"347\" border=\"0\" width=\"260\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">空锅烧油，放葱姜蒜，八角花椒炸出香味后直接倒进苦瓜盆里，盖上盖子放置2个小时以上！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"366\" border=\"0\" width=\"275\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">提示：做的咸点就是咸菜，做的淡点就是凉菜。下粥，吃馒头都很配！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">姑娘『说了这么多，你要给我做了么？』</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">『收！』</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"327\" border=\"0\" width=\"355\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一夫食堂家的菜谱还是蛮容易的嘛！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">做法口诀：切了烫，烫了腌，再浇葱香蒜热油，2小时，么么哒！就是，切的太厚</span><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" width=\"25\" /><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">，然后酱油放的稍多，吃的太急味儿还没够~其他没啥了~</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">这么色香味俱全的蘑菇牌苦瓜，还有这么有逼格的盘子装着，姑娘肯定会爱上我！不要爱上我哟喂！我终于除了握手的份，还能…..！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"431\" border=\"0\" width=\"484\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<a></a><a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">额，万万没有想到….</span></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" height=\"207\" border=\"0\" width=\"280\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<a><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">说到这，还有姑娘愿意试试苦瓜这道菜吗？</span></a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/1/0/981/981_1449489492380.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>',1,429,'2015-12-02 11:29:58',699,'2015-12-07 19:58:15',NULL,NULL,'http://','mogoroom/2015-12/cms/9/2/419/419_1449027418701.jpg',0,0,2),(71,'<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">闺蜜：我从小就只吃蛋白，总想长大后找个只吃蛋黄的老公。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">蘑范范：最后呢？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">闺蜜：结果，老公连鸡蛋都不喜欢....</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">有多少人跟我闺蜜一样，对鸡蛋的喜欢只停留在蛋白层次？想必也有筒子真的只吃蛋黄。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">不过鸡蛋的做法千千种，100%爱它的人吃法可简可繁。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">闺蜜：所以说开始讲做法？</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">蘑范范：当然不是，先从辨别一枚好鸡蛋开始。</span><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">好鸡蛋</span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/0/0/420/420_1449027839303.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">鸡蛋，说白了就是母鸡产的卵，富含胆固醇，味甘性平，从小有多少筒子是1个鸡蛋1杯牛奶过来的？但，你知道一枚好鸡蛋，必须是如图：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/2/2/422/422_1449027896532.JPG\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">有分量：蛋黄圆鼓鼓；紧紧相拥：蛋黄四周的蛋清粘稠，跟蛋黄简直一体；蛋清明显分层，外围较为稀薄！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">闺蜜：照你这么说，打蛋的人最知道什么蛋最好~</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">蘑范范：还真别说，打的一手好蛋，也能让鸡蛋味道更好！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">BUT，鸡蛋简约派根本不用打蛋，他只会这么做：</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">煮鸡蛋</span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"text-indent:2em;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px;\">一枚好鸡蛋，在清洗过后，凉水时放入，然后，1min、2min、3min.......水沸腾后再过多久取出，决定你吃的什么鸡蛋~有多少像我一样爱吃糖心蛋，并且6min不多不少是我的选择。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/4/1/424/424_1449027962314.JPG\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">附上煮鸡蛋时间表，虽然我造88.88888%的简（lan）约(ren)派(pai)对时间毫无概念，但吃货一定要懂！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/9/0/429/429_1449028430109.JPG\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">简约派还有一个选择，当你的冰箱蔬菜肉果各种都光了，相信还有2个鸡蛋会是你的深夜救星，然后还想吃带点咸香口的，那就这么做：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3 align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">炒鸡蛋</span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一口进去，满口蛋香！秘诀就是用中火，让鸡蛋水分刚刚好！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/7/1/427/427_1449028135747.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<h3 align=\"center\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">鸡蛋+</span><span style=\"text-indent:2em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;\">黑松露</span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<p align=\"center\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/6/0/426/426_1449028068396.jpg\" /><br />\r\n	</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">土豪派吃法，上海美食微博“管家的日子”分享过，他们家的馄饨我就不介绍了，炒鸡蛋他配的是黑松露。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 黑松露：富含16种氨基酸，是欧洲人的最爱，跟鹅肝一样的高级存在！黑松露煎蛋算是法国的传统做法，喜欢它的人哪管什么所谓臭鸡蛋气味！吃起来别提多香！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/5/2/425/425_1449028009748.JPG\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<h3>\r\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">鸡蛋+</span></strong><strong style=\"text-indent:2em;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">牛油果</span></strong> \r\n	</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">牛油果对半切，鸡蛋打进去，可挑掉一些蛋白，这样装的下；再来点黑胡椒海盐神马的，烤箱温度180°，15分钟——DING！出炉！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/8/2/428/428_1449028231704.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">蛋黄表面固化，里面还是流质的不能再赞！</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">鸡蛋软饼</span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/1/2/431/431_1449028933071.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果做早餐，爱吃煎饼果子的筒子，在家做个鸡蛋软饼也是不错的选择！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 主料：面粉60g，水100g，鸡蛋1个（爱吃鸡蛋的你再加咯）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 辅料：葱、芝麻和甜面酱，有的时候我选择辣酱，你随意</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/0/1/430/430_1449028885767.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">不要问我面糊怎么做，面糊入锅凝固就可以打上鸡蛋了，再抹匀；撒上黑芝麻和香葱；黑芝麻和香葱粘在蛋液上就可以翻个面，刷甜面酱，ok！吃货还可以加生菜、火腿和油条！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">最后，不管你的男票老公爱不爱吃鸡蛋，下面这道爱心鸡蛋慢慢培养他做起来。适合面色发黄，大姨妈不调的女闺蜜们。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（当归）鸡蛋红糖水</span></strong> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/2/0/432/432_1449029088033.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">当归，一种草本植物的根，性味甘，因为归心、肝和脾，所以也适合女闺蜜大姨妈时吃，补血！擅养生的筒子家里有的话最好了，没有的话一道糖水鸡蛋，也是不错的选择。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/3/1/433/433_1449029379176.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">当归水泡10分钟，用牙刷轻轻刷洗干净，切片（市面上很多直接切片卖，更简单了！）；水煮15分钟；煮熟的鸡蛋剥壳后表皮轻微扎孔，再和当归、红糖一起煮。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><img src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/0/2/980/980_1449489404261.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>',1,429,'2015-12-02 12:13:05',699,'2015-12-07 19:56:58',NULL,NULL,'http://','mogoroom/2015-12/cms/4/2/434/434_1449029585119.jpg',0,0,2),(72,'<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;蘑菇客，指住在蘑菇公寓的优质白领，TA们崇尚自由简约却不简单，对生活品质有要求，有格调有品味具三高特征（学历高，收入高，自我要求高）！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 蘑都明星，挖掘出每一位深藏不露的蘑菇客！说出你的故事，欢迎联系我们！</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#000000;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/0/2/440/440_1449034338754.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/1/0/441/441_1449034344307.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/2/1/442/442_1449034349515.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/3/2/443/443_1449034354561.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\n	<img src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/9/1/979/979_1449489376680.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>',1,429,'2015-12-02 13:34:09',887,'2015-12-08 20:19:13',NULL,NULL,'http://','mogoroom/2015-12/cms/7/2/677/677_1449112725569.jpg',0,0,2),(73,'<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一个穿越百年的相识之旅</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> 一场创意无限的交友派对</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> 一台精英云集的互动盛宴</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> 一幕旗袍佳人的邂逅大戏</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/5/1/445/445_1449042650850.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">民国Love“江南烟雨画屏中，半镜斜窗弄小红。”</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">“夜上海，夜上海，你是个不夜城，华灯起乐声响歌舞升平……”悠扬婉转的爵士音乐，身着旗袍、中山装的美女和绅士手举酒杯，在优雅的音乐和绚丽的灯光中谈笑风生……蘑菇公寓&amp;橄榄餐厅评论“穿越百年遇见你，民国复古风派对” 在华山路黄埔301餐厅华丽上演。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/6/2/446/446_1449042670186.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/7/0/447/447_1449042710778.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">民国风派对里的帅哥，气宇不凡风度翩翩</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/8/1/448/448_1449042734645.jpg\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> 民国风里的旗袍美女，或拥有绝代风华，魅力无人能及</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/mogoroom/2015-12/cms/9/2/449/449_1449042747681.jpg\" />\r\n</p