nt-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我知道你最关心的创始人，</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">不是每天见不了几次面，</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">不是每次见面还得微笑点头甚至鞠一个躬的总裁总经理，</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">就坐在对面那桌可以亲切地直呼其名的！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/imagefile/lehuo_article/1446718346346.jpeg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">我知道你来这里不仅仅是工作！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">生活娱乐当然少不了！因为我们的活动可以这样High！</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/imagefile/lehuo_article/1446718346482.jpeg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">萝莉御姐小鲜肉，猥琐话唠帅大叔。如果这都不是你的菜，没关系，在蘑菇租房工作，联合国并不遥远：美国、英国、马来西亚……因为我们的很多租客是海归白领。所以在这里与世界各国小伙伴们一起生活，这不是梦······</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image.mogoroom.com/imagefile/lehuo